Let's try something new. Let's build a story a few words at a time. Please make each chapter about THREE WORDS long. Be creative and think about where the prior few words were leading. If it starts to get too long, it'll be hard to read so, I'll use a chapter to summarize at somepoint. If you make too long of an entry, I'll delete it.
